Johnny Depp DEMANDS ACLU SHOW PROOF of Amber Heard's Donation | Celebrity Craze

While some celebrities prefer living a quiet life away from the public, others just have so many scandals following them. Johnny Depp has to pay Amber Heard several million in a divorce settlement. Amber Heard said she donated that money to the ACLU because she never wanted Johnny Depp's money. However, many suspected this was not true. Amber might get caught in another lie.
